    <element name="Fury of the Red Dragon" type="Archetype" source="Tanares RPG 5e" id="ID_TRPG_ARCHETYPE_DRAGONBLADE_RED">
        <supports>Dragon Soul</supports>
        <description>
            <p>Dragonblades are the shock troops of the Draconic Council,
and the Fury of the Red Dragon is one of the most aggressive
and intense training styles within their ranks. These warriors
are forged by dragon fire in the art of war and are trained to
lead the assault against their enemies. Those who choose this
path are experts in battle, and their relentless aggression is
unmatched. Whether it be scorching heat or raging infernos, the Fury of the Red Dragon dragonblades are capable
of withstanding the harshest scorching conditions, making
them ideal for missions in South Tanares. They seek to study
the ways of the red dragon and learn from their mastery of
the environment. These warriors are the embodiment of
dragon-like ferocity, and they are feared and respected by
friends and foes alike.</p>
            <p class="indent"></p>
